{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Desktop Blocks is a relaxing desktop game that combines match-3 mechanics with idle gameplay, perfect for a quick break during a busy day. You can play in the corner of your desktop and challenge yourself to clear blocks and score higher. If you're too busy to actively play, you can leave the game running in the background, and it will automatically generate resources over time. You can use these resources to upgrade idle mechanics or unlock skins that suit your style.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Desktop Environment</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Desktop Blocks is a small and compact game designed to run in the corner of your desktop without taking up much space. You can enjoy the fun of block clearing while working on your computer, seamlessly integrating gameplay with your daily tasks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277500/extras/classic_7jm48-n7h1r.gif?t=1731163553\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Idle System</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game will automatically generate Dot resources over time. Even when you're not playing, you can accumulate these resources. Use them to upgrade resource production efficiency, increase inventory capacity, or unlock new skins.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277500/extras/n50na-5aw4n.gif?t=1731163553\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Variety of Skins</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There are a wide variety of skins available in the game, including styles such as retro Windows 98 Paint Tool, pop art, and 8-bit pixel art to meet different aesthetic preferences. Each skin not only changes the appearance of the blocks but also brings a unique visual experience to the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277500/extras/\u5c4f\u5e55\u622a\u56fe_2024-10-05_181506.png?t=1731163553\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"First Skin","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3277500/0284009416a21a03957156a7d7021a400bcd6cb5.jpg"},{"name":"Brave the Difficulty 3","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3277500/0937f871479848694942f7c4fa4456aea9964f4a.jpg"},{"name":"Sweaty at Difficulty 5","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3277500/6496a17b42a1eecd93289abd6507b4cbb8509c1d.jpg"},{"name":"Hello, are you there?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3277500/f771fb80115af042e56587e17ac0cc0e214a2317.jpg"},{"name":"Steal the Developer's Cat","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3277500/93962af42ca73e96a7ce331b68d205bc2a32d9fb.jpg"},{"name":"Dot Millionaire","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3277500/9635793089d7b5fbcbfe66197a75aca711ebd3b2.jpg"},{"name":"Forgot about me?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3277500/075538c045b147999e72bbc1ff2c816fd0339062.jpg"},{"name":"Seven Stars Aligned","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3277500/cb7ea68a491b4debfdb3c347c06a1dd1e7589018.jpg"},{"name":"First Bucket of Dot","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3277500/620a943a3763ceecb1c0b3f0130d15bfac6a75d0.jpg"},{"name":"Become Rich","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3277500/355eb2b5f21c8741c2791b78315e0f2183ace287.jpg"}],"total":10},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277500/page_bg_gene